Step By Step Implementation
---------------------

Access XSIAM and from the left menu navigate to “Settings > Data Sources“ 
![image-1](/images/onboarding/ngfw/1.png)

Then click on the “Add Data Source” button  
![image-2](/images/onboarding/ngfw/2.png)

Search for NGFW (Next Generation Firewall) 
![image-3](/images/onboarding/ngfw/3.png)

Click on “Connect Another Instance” 
![image-4](/images/onboarding/ngfw/4.png)

Make sure the Add NGFW Device checkbox is selected and then search for the Firewall to add by using the search field and the instance ID  
![image-5](/images/onboarding/ngfw/5.png)

Keep selecting other firewalls if required then click “Next” 
![image-6](/images/onboarding/ngfw/6.png)

Select “Connect” and wait of the instance to be imported


